profile:
At New Heights Roofing and Exteriors, we know roofs. We’re experts in keeping your home safe from all of Winnipeg’s extreme weather changes. From rain, to snow, to the blistering heat – we’ve got you covered. Your home is your most valuable investment, so we’ve made it our mission to protect your house from top to bottom.

WE DO NOT SUBCONTRACT. Your home, and most importantly, your family’s protection is too important to let an unknown subcontractor handle your roofing project. Everything from roof installations, to repairs, we do ourselves.

Locally owned and operated, our skill, knowledge and experience positions us to be the best Winnipeg roofing company for quality and price. With efficient and reliable service as the backbone of our company, we ensure each customers needs are met to the highest standards. Our highly skilled installers are experienced and dedicated to the maintenance of your home. We are happy to fulfill your individual wishes. Making it habit to leave a picture prefect job site, a clean yard and a happy home. Making New Heights Roofing and Exteriors your roofing and siding experts, gives you the best combination of top quality installations, at a highly competitive price.
